name: Princess Saho
skill: Increases DMG dealt by 3 allies (ranged priority) by 37%/46% for a limited time.
ability: Moderately increases level when Princess Tatsuta is on the team.
bond: Increases Princess Saho's attack speed by 4%
Increases Princess Tatsuta's attack speed by 4%

additional_data.description: The spirit of Mount Saho, which lies to the east of the ancient capital, Nara. The daughter of a good family that rules spring, and very close with Princess Tatsuta. They are eternal rivals, constantly vying to become more popular than the other. Actually, they perform as an underground idol duo, too. But this is a well-kept secret, and even the Bureau of the Occult doesn't officially recognize it. Lots of people are secretly fans, though. Their music is pretty loud, and she is in charge of vocals and shouting.

main: "Oh, a warm spring day would be so nice..."
